                        <item xml:id="a1"><p><span style="font-size: small"><span style="line-height: 115%"><locus target="#45vb">Fol. 45vb-46</locus>r: Ownership note.</span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"><p style="text-align: justify"><span style="font-size: small"><span style="line-height: 115%">Fol. 45vb: </span></span><span style="font-size: large"><span style="line-height: 115%">&#4829;&#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;&#4961; &#4768;&#4664;&#4653;&#4961; &#4632;&#4725;&#4651;&#4961; &#4848;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4768;&#4616;&#4635;&#4961; &#4845;&#4773;&#4722;&#4961; &#4824;&#4720;&#4643;&#4840;&#4902;&#4961; &#4704;&#4757;&#4811;&#4840;&#4811;&#4961; </span><span style="font-size: small"><span style="line-height: 115%">[fol.</span><span style="line-height: 115%">46r] </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%">&#4708;&#4720;&#4961; &#4781;&#4653;&#4661;&#4722;&#4843;&#4757;&#4961; &#4635;&#4741;&#4704;&#4653;&#4961; &#4768;&#4664;&#4653;&#4961; &#4632;&#4725;&#4651;&#4961; &#4848;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4768;&#4619;&#4635;&#4961; &#4845;&#4773;&#4722;</span></span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note is written in a very crude hand, partly in red. It states that the Ms. was purchased for the money of the church of Maryam ʾAšär Mät(ǝ)ra Däbrä ʾAläma.</p>
